[
  {
    "row": 1,
    "rowsha": "R12wUZ5cXTdUai4u5PFhPuaNSzpwGbru/qlJajaQ9Ik=",
    "originContent": "# fastcompmgr",
    "translatedContent": "# fastcompmgr"
  },
  {
    "row": 2,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 3,
    "rowsha": "cA5gfA7h3pOIyy7xp/vX4XZqEkm+jlBJ+fnFQDjKqng=",
    "originContent": "__fastcompmgr__ is a _fast_ compositor for X, a fork of an early version",
    "translatedContent": "__fastcompmgr__ は X 用の _高速_ コンポジターであり、__Compton__ の初期バージョンのフォークで、"
  },
  {
    "row": 4,
    "rowsha": "FUT6yUto8/ljmqw9tUBzVl030AABYWB0Diw59gZFi1U=",
    "originContent": "of __Compton__ which is a fork of __xcompmgr-dana__ which is a fork",
    "translatedContent": "それは __xcompmgr-dana__ のフォークであり、さらに __xcompmgr__ のフォークです。"
  },
  {
    "row": 5,
    "rowsha": "HVZ+aZsHmCzo4XZxke9MgHB41BTWllNjvy/DKFClhB0=",
    "originContent": "of __xcompmgr__.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 6,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "私は長い間古き良き xcompmgr を使っていました。なぜなら、compton は"
  },
  {
    "row": 7,
    "rowsha": "fRQZaKXUWvbQAcLsWI56/IpXCklXHMaod/dNr5wCFLs=",
    "originContent": "I used to use good old xcompmgr for long, because compton always",
    "translatedContent": "ウィンドウの移動/リサイズやウェブページの慣性スクロール時に"
  },
  {
    "row": 8,
    "rowsha": "TauXmdNV2YqgjdeHhqsgOEO/bg+Uk90UD8HnSnXzl6k=",
    "originContent": "felt a bit laggy when moving/resizing windows or kinetic-scrolling",
    "translatedContent": "少し遅延を感じていたからです。最新の picom-10.2 を試してみると、状況はさらに"
  },
  {
    "row": 9,
    "rowsha": "I7Sg12xozTGGVwJILdTdfgYsClawxP4R7aT3DGlCf5s=",
    "originContent": "a webpage. Having tested the latest picom-10.2, it seems, things got even",
    "translatedContent": "悪化しているようでした（下記のベンチマーク参照）。しかし、xcompmgr は argb ウィンドウ（例：一部の端末）に"
  },
  {
    "row": 10,
    "rowsha": "FlobFnHyIm8fhuyNqYHs15C0r6/Sq3jpgYo5cZOXhRw=",
    "originContent": "worse (see benchmark below). However, xcompmgr does not draw shadows",
    "translatedContent": "影を描画せず、他にもいくつかの不具合があります。そこで私は 2011 年まで遡り、"
  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "B+0d9k5wcsokts25WIGNe5qmrT9dezXx225HlBpgtDs=",
    "originContent": "on argb windows (e.g. some terminals) and",
    "translatedContent": "この機能が追加された時点のコードを取り出し、後の compton のコミットからいくつかを選んで"
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "OZxJ7Tcv6R3cZOY3rHZMWzTPIDa6cUe748397xsDKFc=",
    "originContent": "has several other glitches. That's why I traveled back into 2011, where",
    "translatedContent": "不要なセグフォルトやメモリリークを取り除き、プロファイリングに基づいてそのバージョンをさらに"
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "oRn5TkcETPrUfTeoHoR4EHx/SVQdFBA/+P1D8b7et+M=",
    "originContent": "this feature was just added, cherry picked some later compton commits",
    "translatedContent": "高速化しました。"
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "JSqZbxHKmKlyTS6RGDrGkMMT+075PpxUJ2QtbDZCu30=",
    "originContent": "to get rid of spurious segfaults and memleaks and made that version even",
    "translatedContent": "例えば、ウィンドウの移動およびリサイズイベントはイベント数を制限し、"
  },
  {
    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "z/UWEIfpQbBdDAooQidZikM92l1nZWrpU8OAqtyZ92M=",
    "originContent": "faster, based on profiling.",
    "translatedContent": "ある程度固定のフレームレートで描画される一方で、"
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "ipaxbhwwGM7y1BczD7nL39y6K72PHFLNj62d9dUbHfw=",
    "originContent": "For example, window move- and resize events are limited in their",
    "translatedContent": "スクロールは可能な限り高速に行われます。隠れているウィンドウは描画されず、"
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "86EuETKt9ZoGuo3oedxVww+MX6MdRbJYPjwIs8hNOtA=",
    "originContent": "event-count and rendered at a somewhat fixed framerate, while",
    "translatedContent": "メモリの割り当て/解放は大幅に回避されているため、"
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "GdbP4dLIES9DuRd2Pz3+5yOvVk9ilWTJv6Mfj7/Q90s=",
    "originContent": "scrolling is still done as fast as possible. Occluded windows are not",
    "translatedContent": "画面の再描画が高速になります。"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "ApXAtAfl0+6t8/6hpIFKQCW2uFqdcCQMXXlMHOHxcDc=",
    "originContent": "painted and memory allocations/deallocations are largely avoided,",
    "translatedContent": "欠点としては、フェード機能は現在壊れており（私は使っていません）、申し訳ありません (; "
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "BqwQ7sSW0/AcrYIL6We8YYA7df+QzZEybK8lqSOTULY=",
    "originContent": "allowing for faster repaints of the screen.",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "Q3hzdFXw3i0A2xdOght+uJ6MuxkmlFupzEY6vEDcfVU=",
    "originContent": "On the downside, fading is currently broken (I don't use it). Sorry",
    "translatedContent": "## ベンチマーク"
  },
  {
    "row": 22,
    "rowsha": "gp5gG6nNhYAwcCd6BOCGTLYAJ6BWM/QKRWvXHTn7k5U=",
    "originContent": "for that (;",
    "translatedContent": "私の Dell Latitude E5570 上でのウィンドウの移動、リサイズ、スクロールは"
  },
  {
    "row": 23,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "明らかに高速に「感じられ」、この観察を裏付けるいくつかの数値もあります。"
  },
  {
    "row": 24,
    "rowsha": "Ef0UsiyD6h8Bsal0VWE7OxxQZOlWCfTesTDl7PDsG1Y=",
    "originContent": "## Benchmark",
    "translatedContent": "複数の chromium ウィンドウを重ねた状態で、どのウィンドウも完全に隠れていない状況で、"
  },
  {
    "row": 25,
    "rowsha": "GOqcOMlCJugL8NYZ3ir5KtoTnJoKfFko5VSnK1tUk9c=",
    "originContent": "While on my Dell Latitude E5570 window moving, resizing and scrolling",
    "translatedContent": "それぞれの操作を *手動で* 実施しましたので、"
  },
  {
    "row": 26,
    "rowsha": "FiHA76o/h9bgV12fRGtEZ/q5o/xArwCgZZCk7PWsqRQ=",
    "originContent": "*feels* clearly faster, there are also some numbers to support this",
    "translatedContent": "このベンチマークはあまり高度ではないことにご注意ください。慣性スクロールを可能にする"
  },
  {
    "row": 27,
    "rowsha": "2SZVfoS8ApsMzm1MWZCStWnUXavIqt+odV6SSrVLYUU=",
    "originContent": "observation. Given a number of stacked chromium-windows, where no window",
    "translatedContent": "タッチパッドドライバー `xserver-xorg-input-synaptics` を使用しました（Wayland はどうでしょう？）。"
  },
  {
    "row": 28,
    "rowsha": "50LTR9cwbRxQGhuPaQ75fzutRiG4rhuOGvnD6xOs3Zo=",
    "originContent": "is fully occluded, I performed the respective operations *by hand*,",
    "translatedContent": "以下の CPU 使用率が計測されました："
  },
  {
    "row": 29,
    "rowsha": "ggLTdjPN/2RU8gNcUv5rPM78gA4Qw/q8svkx9PA+myY=",
    "originContent": "so please beware that the benchmark is not very sophisticated. The touchpad",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 30,
    "rowsha": "3GSRGkNpjSgmmpU5l6TPbcBVUQxPCNHtv+YXdVGQGrE=",
    "originContent": "driver `xserver-xorg-input-synaptics` was used which enables for kinetic",
    "translatedContent": "| コンポジター    | 移動  | リサイズ  | スクロール |"
  },
  {
    "row": 31,
    "rowsha": "6sUm8ZOacEiRWPg1tmMPGBKBkW4HCnvmc+6At99oDco=",
    "originContent": "scrolling (Wayland anyone?). The following CPU usages were measured:",
    "translatedContent": "| ------------- | ----- | ------- | ------ |"
  },
  {
    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "| fastcompmgr   | 6.7%  | 4.4%    | 1.5%   |"
  },
  {
    "row": 33,
    "rowsha": "nU+nc/vNy7OL64v8/yyPpqnDdUU8isE/d+gELIRBB0o=",
    "originContent": "| Compositor    | move  | resize  | scroll |",
    "translatedContent": "| xcompmgr      | 7.8%  | 4.9%    | 1.6%   |"
  },
  {
    "row": 34,
    "rowsha": "xABU9XYG+nYwO058M8Rnrw0bNZtPbXI7zzsbFYiGmds=",
    "originContent": "| ------------- | ----- | ------- | ------ |",
    "translatedContent": "| compton       | 26.4% | 6.8%    | 17.1%  |"
  },
